{
  "stem": "6052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [? as ?] [? said ?] from there I went to Steckelsdorf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was a place near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Before, I said near Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What is still memorable was that it was terribly cold when I went there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had to work long hours and hard work in all agricultural matters to help the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was not-- not to help with-- not to prepare us for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was more-- this is why it was kind of exempted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was kind of a forced labor in a different name, which it was called at that time Hachshara.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I was there, and it was a terrible place to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And over there I felt the hardship, more than even before in Leipzig, because it was so miserable.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And another hardship, of course, when I escaped, and we escaped, and we came to Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Before we came to Zagreb, to go over the border was such hardship also, because we had to go over hills and [INAUDIBLE] in all kinds of conditions.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it was a danger by itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this also contributed to what I mentioned before, that I wrote my mother that my sister should not-- or my sisters-- should not attempt to do the same because I was afraid of-- of something will happen to them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this was even-- [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been-- ?] we were travelling from Graz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Graz was our border town, and I believe in Yugoslavia it was Maribor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the other border town where we came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to roll down a big hill-- which was dangerous by itself-- wrapped in-- in-- in kind of wrapped sheets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And coming down the hill was by itself a matter of danger.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
